WEBVTT

00:01.130 --> 00:03.330
Shri Krishna Puja
Cabella Ligure, Italy

00:03.330 --> 00:04.430
August 16, 1992

08:33.900 --> 08:39.900
Today we have decided to have the puja of
Shri Krishna.

08:39.900 --> 08:52.819
We have many a times done this puja and have
understood the essence of Shri Krishna’s

08:52.819 --> 08:56.799
advent, which was six thousand years back.

08:56.799 --> 09:15.800
And now, what His manifestation was, what
He wanted to be accomplished has to be done

09:15.800 --> 09:20.110
in this Kali Yuga.

09:20.110 --> 09:31.790
As it is, this Kali Yuga is going into a new
realm of Satya Yuga, but in between there

09:31.790 --> 09:44.479
is Krita Yuga where this Brahmachaitanya,
or we can say the all-pervading Power of God’s

09:44.479 --> 09:47.600
love, is going to act.

09:47.600 --> 09:58.670
At this time, what is going to happen with
Shri Krishna’s powers – this is what we

09:58.670 --> 10:01.100
have to see.

10:01.100 --> 10:07.119
Shri Krishna, as I told you, was the incarnation
also of diplomacy.

10:07.119 --> 10:16.179
So He plays around quite a lot, and ultimately
He brings forth the untruth and the falsehood;

10:16.179 --> 10:18.229
but in doing that He judges people.

10:18.229 --> 10:26.579
So it’s very important that Shri Krishna’s
powers of His diplomacy were to be manifesting

10:26.579 --> 10:32.109
at this time, when it is the Last Judgment.

10:32.109 --> 10:45.960
So now whatever we have done wrong before,
whatever karmas which have been done in ignorance

10:45.960 --> 10:53.690
maybe, or maybe deliberately, all of them
will be paid back.

10:53.690 --> 11:01.910
Those punyas which you have done in previous
lives, this life, will be also rewarded.

11:01.910 --> 11:10.570
This is all done through Shri Krishna’s
principles of collectivity, where He collectively

11:10.570 --> 11:13.840
sees the situation.

11:13.840 --> 11:26.050
For example, as I told you last time also
that Columbus luckily went to America; luckily,

11:26.050 --> 11:30.870
so we were saved, otherwise we would not have
been here.

11:30.870 --> 11:40.310
And then these Spanish people, bullfighters,
they went and started fighting the poor, unarmed

11:40.310 --> 11:46.680
people who were just very simple owners of
that land.

11:46.680 --> 11:52.570
But they went and occupied those lands, and
killed every one of them.

11:52.570 --> 11:57.980
So in America you can’t find anyone, no
doubt, but even in South America you have

11:57.980 --> 12:05.390
to go to Colombia or to Bolivia, to great
heights, to see some aboriginals there; otherwise

12:05.390 --> 12:08.940
most of them are finished.

12:08.940 --> 12:14.060
So now in Krita Yuga all these diseases have
started cropping up.

12:14.060 --> 12:22.130
But the best part is the drug addiction.

12:22.130 --> 12:31.700
These drugs are made, for your information,
in Bolivia and in Colombia.

12:31.700 --> 12:39.860
You drove them down there, so now you have
the drugs and very nicely you are very welcoming

12:39.860 --> 12:41.590
them.

12:41.590 --> 12:53.010
People went in Nicaragua to help them and
brought back all these horrible drugs to Washington;

12:53.010 --> 12:58.730
and in every elite society they are just discussing
which is the best drug, where is the sale

12:58.730 --> 13:02.630
on and where should they buy the drugs.

13:02.630 --> 13:08.990
So the all of America is now worried how much
drug they can import, and kill themselves

13:08.990 --> 13:11.560
and destroy themselves.

13:11.560 --> 13:17.720
So this destruction has started from inside.

13:17.720 --> 13:24.570
Then in addition to that, when I went there
first I told them not to indulge into these

13:24.570 --> 13:40.540
Freudian practices but keep to morality, otherwise
you’ll have problems.

13:40.540 --> 13:52.790
So they had first AIDS, secondly now yuppie’s
disease, and all kinds of secret diseases

13:52.790 --> 13:55.370
they have.

13:55.370 --> 14:00.609
Among ten people there would be at least one
person who is suffering from that, and among

14:00.609 --> 14:05.870
twenty people there’ll be at least one person
who must be suffering from schizophrenia.

14:05.870 --> 14:14.950
Because they made every person, every other
country nervous, so now they are getting schizophrenia.

14:14.950 --> 14:20.200
Like this we can see even in England.

14:20.200 --> 14:32.210
Now in England they came to India as traders,
ordinary traders, and plundered us completely,

14:32.210 --> 14:38.370
no doubt, ruled us for three hundred years
– as I say, it’s gracious hospitality

14:38.370 --> 14:46.070
they had – and then they left us in three
pieces.

14:46.070 --> 14:50.810
And now in their own country there are problems,
all kinds.

14:50.810 --> 14:58.980
First of all nobody wants to call themselves
as English; they all call themselves Welsh

14:58.980 --> 15:03.680
or Scots, or specially the Irish.

15:03.680 --> 15:08.340
And there is always a bomb scare in London,
every time, and for our first program also

15:08.340 --> 15:11.109
there was a bomb scare.

15:11.109 --> 15:17.280
So you can imagine these English who tried
to divide us are automatically divided among

15:17.280 --> 15:19.730
themselves, and now fighting each other.

15:19.730 --> 15:26.160
But there are other problems also like AIDS
and immoral life, everything like that.

15:26.160 --> 15:28.490
Same with the French.

15:28.490 --> 15:35.790
French tried to sell their wine all over,
and bring their horrible bathroom culture

15:35.790 --> 15:36.990
everywhere.

15:36.990 --> 15:39.600
Now they are suffering from it.

15:39.600 --> 15:45.389
For example, most of the time they’re drunk
and they have lost all moorings, I mean, they

15:45.389 --> 15:47.780
have no sense left in their heads.

15:47.780 --> 15:53.740
Like a housewife could be a prostitute – allowed
by law.

15:53.740 --> 15:56.590
