This is also Shri Krishna’s power, because
He’s Kubera.

16:12.100 --> 16:15.750
He’s the one who is the power of wealth.

16:15.750 --> 16:21.980
He gave lot of wealth to all these countries,
and now they don’t know what to do with

16:21.980 --> 16:22.980
themselves.

